{"tid":472022,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家繼續用支那機！","createTime":"2017-11-17T20:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T16:48:53.000Z","uid":47027,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2db1bba2ff8bf05129f9c5f0991e3024bd53931e","tid":472022,"uid":47027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T20:34:46.000Z","msg":"【有國產手機可竊取個人資料】<br />\n【原有程式碼被改動】<br />\n<br />\n美國高通Qualcomm工程師Alex Gantman 在Twitter 上留言，指經過高通內部調查後，發現國產OnePlus 手機內由高通提供的程式碼被人為地改動過。<br />\n<br />\n有業內人士說，這樣的改動，令該牌子不同型號手機出現「後門」，第三者或黑客很容易獲得手機的Root 權限， 用以截取手機Wi-Fi、藍牙、定位、NFC 等裝置的使用情況，甚至複制手機內的相片、影片等個人資料。<br />\n<br />\nOnePlus製造商目前未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#國產手機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1561247050686442&amp;id=265944843550009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1561247050686442%26id%3D265944843550009&d=Fy44ZujKm9oT4Thc8K%2FcJYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=267867c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1561247050686442&amp;id=265944843550009</a><br />\n<br />\n#連登仔口裏說不，身體卻很誠實！"},{"pid":"0c694384d5faed65d261c4901c3cc2bd2d9c17b9","tid":472022,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"中國電話，送都唔用"},{"pid":"9cbfebd0e2c3dcb1b823fbf9c3bf961c7a53a28d","tid":472022,"uid":1130,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"鬼佬幾鍾意Oneplus架wo 呢單野唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望雷蛇果部會彈起"},{"pid":"435611adc920fdcef829cb7c7d2091719a913aad","tid":472022,"uid":5686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼佬幾鍾意Oneplus架wo 呢單野唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望雷蛇果部會彈起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真Razer 果部會死得好慘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7